{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Lower the State Pension age to free up jobs for young adults",
        "additional_details": "The longer people are having to work the fewer jobs there are out there for young adults. If the Government lowered the State Pension age we believe it could encourage retirement so that employers might take on a young adult to fill the space \u2013 that would help young people get jobs and also help the older generation that have done their bit for society and get to enjoy the last few years of their life.",
        "background": "Lower the State Pension age for workers so young adults that don't currently work have more chance of getting a job.",
